import React from 'react'
import {
    ServicesContainer,
    ServicesH1,
    ServicesH2,
    ServicesWrapper,
    ServicesCard,
    ServicesIcon,
    ServicesP,
} from './ServiceElements';

const Services = () => {
    return (
        <ServicesContainer id="services">
            <ServicesH1>Our Clients</ServicesH1>
            <ServicesWrapper>
                <ServicesCard>
                    <ServicesIcon src={Icon1} />
                    <ServicesH2>Reduce Expenses</ServicesH2>
                    <ServicesP>Help reduce fees and increase revenue</ServicesP>
                </ServicesCard>
                <ServicesCard>
                    <ServicesIcon src={Icon2} />
                    <ServicesH2>Virtual Reality</ServicesH2>
                    <ServicesP>Access platform online anywhere in the world</ServicesP>
                </ServicesCard>
                <ServicesCard>
                    <ServicesIcon src={Icon3} />
                    <ServicesH2>Premium Benefits</ServicesH2>
                    <ServicesP>Unlock special perks with membership that reutrns 5% cashback</ServicesP>
                </ServicesCard>
            </ServicesWrapper>
        </ServicesContainer>
    )
}

export default Services;
